flowchart TD
    subgraph Apps["1000+ Microservices"]
        API["API services"]
        Workers["Workers"]
        Crons["CronJobs"]
    end

    Apps -->|OTel SDK| Alloy["Alloy DaemonSet"]

    Alloy --> PII["PII Redaction: cedula, NIT, cards, emails"]

    PII -->|Metrics| Mimir["Mimir - S3 backend"]
    PII -->|Logs| Loki["Loki - S3 backend"]
    PII -->|Traces 10pct| Tempo["Tempo - S3 backend"]

    Mimir --> Grafana["Grafana HA"]
    Loki --> Grafana
    Tempo --> Grafana

    subgraph SLO["SLO Pipeline"]
        Spec["slo.yaml per service"] --> Sloth["Sloth generator"]
        Sloth --> Rules["PrometheusRules"]
        Rules --> Burn["Burn-rate alerts"]
    end

    Rules -->|Recording rules| Mimir

    Burn -->|14x burn| PD["PagerDuty page"]
    Burn -->|6x burn| Slack["Slack notify"]

    Mimir -->|Query| AR["Argo Rollouts AnalysisRun"]
    AR --> Gate{"PASS?"}
    Gate -->|Yes| Advance["Advance canary"]
    Gate -->|No| Rollback["Auto-rollback"]

    DT["Dependency-Track"] -.->|CVE alerts| Slack

    style Apps fill:#bbdefb,stroke:#1565c0
    style Alloy fill:#c8e6c9,stroke:#2e7d32
    style PII fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#f9a825
    style SLO fill:#e1bee7,stroke:#7b1fa2
    style Rollback fill:#ffcccc,stroke:#c62828
